cff-version: 1.2.0
message: If you use this work, please cite it using the metadata below.
type: dataset
title: L2 Forwarding Latency Measurements Dataset
abstract: This dataset contains results from experiments measuring L2 forwarding latency
  using a load generator script (MoonGen) across multiple configurations. The methodology
  involved running tests with varying packet rates and sizes on the target device
  under test, capturing associated logs for analysis. Evaluation focused on deriving
  performance metrics including latency measurements and energy consumption data during
  execution.
